name: Urban MRT - Crypto Apocalyptic Train
description:
We made this Urban Crypto Train because in the post apocalyptic world some creatures also need to get from A to B.  

Collaboration Art by JaSha made X UNN0NRM4L.Studio

UNN0RM4L Artist: JaSha made, hand drawn design to GIF animation.

UNN0RM4L.Studio collective of less fortunate or non crypto nerd artist that still produce distinctive and brilliant art pieces.

Because the basic knowledge of the #crypto #NFT world is missing, we aim to give them a chance to shine bright and be discovered in this beautiful modern world.

100% going to the artist or their families.
